2007-08-26 Raffaella Traniello   

    * 1.47.EN - 1.46.pt_BR 
    
    * 1.47.EN
    
    Chapter 1: Introduction
    - Updated edition number
    - Removed Main Actor from the list of recommended software since maintenance and distribution have been discontinued (see http://www.mainconcept.com/site/consumer-products-4/mainactor-v5-15/information-16.html)
    - Removed Moxy from the list of recommended software(No longer being developed - see http://www.linuxartist.org/video-anim.html)
    - Added Avidemux and Kdenlive (and relative links)
    - Added node 358: HOWTOs
    - Added two howto on creating fancy titles (by David McNab and Gustavo Iniguez Goya).
    - Added an howto on Chromakey (HSV) plugin (by Jerome Cornet)
    
    Chapter 2: Installation
    - Minor changes
    - Added "or 60Mb for a read-only checkout" in Usual Compilation Process (by gray-DokuWiki) 
    - Minor changes in Arch Linux
    - Ubuntu repos: added Core Duo Intel64 as AMD64 compatible
    - Added packages list for compilation in Debian (by mcarter-Dokuwiki)
    
    Chapter 5: Loading and saving files
    - Improved the description of changing paths from absolute to relative and viceversa
    - Added description of repair of broken media linkage from the GUI.
    - Added @cindex Paths
    
    Chapter 7: Editing
    - minor changes
    - Added @index Three points editing to Two screen editing
    
    Chapter 14: Realtime effects
    - Added hints for animating titles and keyframes support.
    
   
    * 1.46.pt_BR
    
    - Updated to ed. 1.46 (by Flavio Soares)
    
    
