2007-06-21 Raffaella Traniello  

    * 1.35.EN (Ed 1.33b)

    Merged the changes made on Dokuwiki Chapters 13,17 between 03/04/07 and 21/06/07
    Chapter 1: Introduction
    - Added Hermann Vosseler in the contributors list.
    Chapter 13: Realtime effects
    - Description and typical usage scenario for "Frames to fields". By ichthyostega.
    - Descritpion for the gradient plugin. By ichthyostega.
    - Details on the parameters of the HSV plugin. By ichthyostega.
    - Correction: Descriptions of "interpolate pixels" belongs to the "interpolate video" effect. By ichthyostega.
    - Descritpion for the overlay video plugin. By ichthyostega.
    - A warning for usage of Translate effect on interlaced footage. By ichthyostega.
    - Correction of Unsharp Effect description: bring in the well known name "unsharp mask", because it's not just softening or blurring... By  ichthyostega.
    Chapter 17: Keyframing
    - Added a note about deleting ganged keyframes. By raffa.


