2007-01-15  Nicolas Maufrais  <e.conti@gmx.net>

	* 1.02.EN
	  - Remove image manual_images_en/track_attributes in node "Supported
	    file formats". That image was not at the right place.
	  - Add information in the "Loading other formats" node to explain how
	    to identify any video s codecs and container (using mplayer -identify xyz)
	  - Add a link to Scott Frase s "Beginner s Guide to Exporting Video
	    from Cinelerra", in the tutorials node, as suggested by Scott in his
	    mail to the mailing-list (Date: Mon, 15 Jan 2007 15:25:30 +0000)
	  - Add links to 2 tutorials ("Capturando e editando video usando Software Livre"
	    and "Tutorial Cinelerra") as suggested by Rafael Diniz in his mail
	    to the mailing-list (Date: Sat, 13 Jan 2007 02:31:46 -0200)
	  - Add a link to www.100fps.com in the tutorials node. It is an
	    interesting page about deinterlacing, suggested by Raffaella Traniello.
	  - Add a link in the "Tutorials" node to "Edicion de video bajo
	    GNU/Linux (Cinelerra)", in Spanish, by Gustavo Iniguez Goya
	  - Add a link in the Ubuntu node to the following page
	    www.kiberpipa.org/~gandalf/blog/?p=65
	* 1.02.FR
	  - Up-to-date with 1.02.EN
