	    highlighted region to the previous label." to
	    "@kbd{SHIFT-CTRL-LEFT} highlights the region between the insertion
	    point and the previous label."
	  - Raffaella Traniello - Change "@kbd{SHIFT-CTRL-RIGHT} extends the
	    highlighted region to the next label." to "@kbd{SHIFT-CTRL-RIGHT}
	    highlights the region between the insertion point and the next
	    label."
