2006-12-05  Nicolas Maufrais  <e.conti@gmx.net>

	* Edition 0.58
	  - Formatting fix in node "Making a DVD"
	  - New formatting changes in the plugins node
	  - Correct a wrong reference in Compositing
	  - Replace @example by @code, since blank lines are inserted before
	    and after @example commands. That produces ugly html output.
	  - Replace "Then make like Win 2000 and reboot" by "Then reboot"
	  - Add an @itemize in node "Speeding up the hard drive"
	  - Add the word "option" which was missing in one sentence of the
	    "Install Cinelerra CV" paragraph
	  - Reformat the notes located in the "Usual compilation process" node
	  - Move information regarding .po files not being installed when
	    specifying a prefix different from the default
	  - Add an xref to "Usual compilation process" in "Environment
	    variables"
	  - Subsubsub-sectionning of the "Still images" node
	  - Remove images/slider.png

